Package registration

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ICheckRegistration
    Represents an interface that takes in a student and a camp name, and returns a value of true or false based on his registration details.
    IDeregisterCamp
    Represents an interface that takes in a student and a camp name, and deregisters the student in the registration database.
    IGetCampNamesRolesRegistered
    Represents an interface that returns all camp names that a student is registered in, and his respective roles.
    IGetCampsIsCommittee
    Represents an interface that returns all camp names that a student is a camp committee member of.
    IGetCampsRegistered
    Represents an interface that returns all camp names that a student has registered in.
    IGetStudentNamesRolesRegistered
    Represents an interface that returns an ArrayList of ArrayList of Strings containing all the students and their corresponding roles in a given camp.
    IRegisterCamp
    Represents an interface that registers a student to a camp, not including camp committee member.
    IRegisterCommittee
    Represents an interface that registers a student to a Camp as a camp committee member.
    IViewRegisteredCamps
    Represents an interface that allows a student to interact with the associated registration database to print the details of all his registered camps.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AttendeeRegistrationChecker
    Represents a class that helps to check if a student is registered as an attendee in a given camp.
    CommitteeCampRegisterer
    Represents a class that helps to register a student into a camp as a camp committee member.
    CommitteeRegistrationChecker  
    ListOfCampsIsCommiteeOfGetter
    Represents an class that manages the registration database and allows clients to request for a list of camps that a student has registered as a committee member of in the registration database.
    RegisteredCampNamesGetter
    Represents an class that manages the registration database and allows clients to request for a list of camp names that a student has registered for, regardless of role in the registration database.
    RegisteredCampNamesRolesGetter
    Represents an class that manages the registration database and allows clients to provide a student name, and request for a list containing a list of Strings that contains information on the camp name, and the corresponding role of the student in that camp.
    RegisteredStudentNamesRolesGetter
    Represents an class that manages the registration database and allows clients to provide a camp name, and request for a list containing a list of Strings that contains information on the student name, and the corresponding role of the student in that camp.
    Registration
    Represents a Registration entry created in the registration database.
    RegistrationDataBase
    Represents a Registration Database.
    StudentCampDeregisterer
    Represents an class that manages the registration database and allows clients to deregister from a camp.
    StudentCampRegisterer
    Represents an class that manages the registration database and allows clients to register for a camp as a camp attendee.
    StudentRegisteredCampsViewer
    Represents an class that manages the registration database and allows clients to view all the camp details that a student has registered for, as well as his corresponding.
